title: Phonero Bedriftsnett

creator: Phonero
descriptionHtml:
Get the most important features of Phonero Bedriftsnett on your phone for a more efficient workday:
- Home screen where you can add the most important features and shortcuts
- Always updated company catalogue with availability status and away notification
- Update your call forwarding setup connected to each of the availability profiles
- White and yellow page lookup, call log and full overview of lost queue calls
- Setup and change number display and what devices you want to answer calls on
- View your queues and log in and out of queues
- Messaging module with distribution lists
- Phone Conference
- Queue administration

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Will display Teams presence in Company Catalogue if Teams integrations exist for company.
- Added support for queue administration.
- Minor bugfixes and improvements.
